5
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:04,120
Excuse me.

6
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,640
Was that...

7
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,740
That was Eighth Young Master.

8
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:11,950
Master Zang, please don't keep our Mistress waiting.

9
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:22,160
Miss, Master Zang is here.

10
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,280
Miss Xiang.

11
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:35,460
How coincidental.

12
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:39,050
I just got back, just in time to catch you sending gifts.

13
00:02:39,050 --> 00:02:43,710
What? Are you in need of my Zhen Tower's help so soon?

14
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:48,930
Please forgive me. I'm here to make amends.

15
00:02:48,930 --> 00:02:52,300
I was too arrogant before and failed to appreciate your kindness.

16
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:55,020
I betrayed your good intentions.

17
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:58,800
Is it too late to change my mind now?

18
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:03,610
Didn't you say you weren't worthy of my friendship?

19
00:03:03,610 --> 00:03:06,260
Why have you changed your mind now?

20
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:09,010
Did earning the Marquis's trust make you think

21
00:03:09,010 --> 00:03:11,680
you've risen above?

22
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:17,300
I wouldn't mention trust.

23
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:21,510
I'd be lucky if the Marquis isn't suspicious of me.

24
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:26,390
I've been deeply harmed by the rumors from these past few days.

25
00:03:26,390 --> 00:03:28,770
So, that's why you're here?

26
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:32,120
What rumors? How come I haven't heard anything?

27
00:03:32,690 --> 00:03:36,260
Miss Xiang, please have mercy on me.

28
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:38,580
The rumors from Eighth Young Master...

29
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:40,480
Who said they came from him?

30
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:42,740
This has nothing to do with Zhen Tower.

31
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:43,740
Fine...

32
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:48,080
Then let's say it has nothing to do with Zhen Tower, and the rumors didn't start here.

33
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:51,280
I came today to ask for your help

34
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:55,410
in putting an end to those rumors.

35
00:03:56,860 --> 00:04:00,850
Rumors blow over like the wind.

36
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:08,770
The wind fades, but the damage remains.

37
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:11,330
Rumors stick in people's minds.

38
00:04:11,330 --> 00:04:16,330
As they spread, people forget where they heard them

39
00:04:16,330 --> 00:04:20,480
and just assume they're true.

40
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,770
You care that much?

41
00:04:21,770 --> 00:04:26,960
The Marquis said he'd get to the bottom of this.

42
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,700
Are you threatening me with his name?

43
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,530
I wouldn't dare.

44
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:36,500
But if you're truly blameless and unwilling to help,

45
00:04:38,770 --> 00:04:41,270
I'll have to leave it to fate.

46
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,040
You overestimate me.

47
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:48,000
I doubt I have the power to convince Eighth Young Master.

48
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:55,540
I'm certain you can move him.

49
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:07,940
Zang Hai, if you want to chase power and success,

50
00:05:07,940 --> 00:05:11,360
there are plenty of powerful men in the capital to rely on.

51
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:17,650
You don't go to them. Why are you so fixated on serving the Marquis of Pingjin?

52
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:22,970
Back then, because of the Empress Dowager's burial,

53
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:26,560
he was looking for feng shui masters and seized me.

54
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:31,520
I was just a commoner. To survive, I had no choice.

55
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,830
I was just like a drowning man

56
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:36,460
clutching a floating branch in the currents

57
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,850
and trying to make it out alive.

58
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:45,460
It just so happened that the branch turned out to be a towering tree.

59
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:50,510
If you ask me, he didn't choose you.

60
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:53,360
Rather, you chose him.

61
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:59,460
Sounds like you care quite a bit as well.

62
00:06:16,940 --> 00:06:20,830
In the capital, relationships form a tight web.

63
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:25,020
Grudges and favors between people are like hidden rocks in the river.

64
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:27,680
You can't see or feel them

65
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,980
until your boat hits one.

66
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:36,630
Well said. I'll keep that in mind.

67
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:40,560
But rest assured. I won't become your enemy.

68
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:44,100
Our goals don't clash.

69
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:47,600
That's not for you to decide.

70
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:52,160
Miss Xiang, just wait and see.

71
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:57,700
I'll be here in the capital, accepting the surveillance of you and everyone else.

72
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,140
Who'd want to watch you?

73
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:02,720
Whether you turn out to be good or bad has nothing to do with me.

74
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,560
 Chili peppers! 
   

75
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:10,140
That stall belongs to a Dongxia merchant.

76
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:19,460
Dongxia and the Great Yong trade regularly.

77
00:07:19,460 --> 00:07:21,770
But it's tough doing business here now,

78
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:24,850
and the Imperial Surveillance Office is always watching.

79
00:07:24,850 --> 00:07:31,250
He's just like you said. Without realizing it, he was under the watchful eyes of many.

80
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:38,730
Never mind. You just made yourself sound so pitiful.

81
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:40,240
If I don't let you go,

82
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,930
wouldn't I be as awful as the Imperial Surveillance Office?

83
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,970
Your gifts today cost you a great deal.

84
00:07:45,970 --> 00:07:48,810
I'll talk to Eighth Young Master for you.

85
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:53,030
Thank you, Miss Xiang.

86
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:56,950
I'll take my leave.

87
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:13,850
Young Master, what would you like? Have a look around.

88
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:18,390
 Candied hawthorn! 

89
00:08:19,030 --> 00:08:23,830
These are handmade, embroidered with Dongxia patterns.

90
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:26,470
Would you like one?

91
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:30,900
I'll take this one.

92
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:33,950
Thank you, Young Master. Thank you!

93
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:40,720
You're letting him off so easily?

94
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:44,790
Didn't you want to sabotage his career

95
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:47,600
and get him kicked out of the capital?

96
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,320
I can't figure him out.

97
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:54,380
From what he's saying, it seems the rumors helped him gain more trust from the Marquis of Pingjin.

98
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:56,400
He really is something.

99
00:08:57,010 --> 00:08:59,380
Now you're admiring his talent?

100
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:03,030
He ignored my warning, so why should I bother?

101
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:06,480
We'll see how things go. The real show's still to come.

102
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,630
 Fresh cakes! 

103
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:12,080
 Hot and sweet! 

104
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:27,320
Master.

105
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:31,300
You didn't even discuss something as big as assassinating the Marquis of Pingjin with me?

106
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:35,920
Your wings have hardened. You've learned to act on your own volition.

107
00:09:37,570 --> 00:09:41,200
Master, I was wrong.

108
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:44,450
I was going to ask for your advice,

109
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:47,100
but someone knocked me out and took me away.

110
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:50,290
When I awoke, I saw my senior brother, Guan Feng.

111
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:53,620
He was also working at the Marquis's mansion.

112
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:59,410
   

113
00:09:59,410 --> 00:10:02,400
So much has happened.

114
00:10:03,530 --> 00:10:06,790
Good thing the rumors are cleared,

115
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:09,100
and the Marquis has lowered his guard against you.

116
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:11,480
Zhen Tower really is powerful.

117
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:15,100
They nearly ruined you with just a rumor.

118
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:17,200
We can't kill the Marquis now.

119
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,290
I need to keep serving him to find out who the third person is.

120
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:23,170
Since it was three people plotting together,

121
00:10:23,170 --> 00:10:28,260
my guess is they're of similar standing.

122
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,930
Not necessarily.

123
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:34,920
It's been years. Officials rise and fall.

124
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:38,140
Someone will slip through the net.

125
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:45,570
We cannot rule out a noble, a rich merchant, or even a commoner.

126
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:49,350
I didn't think of that.

127
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:52,950
If so, the investigation could take forever.

128
00:10:56,770 --> 00:11:00,140
If only the Marquis would just tell us himself.

129
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:02,630
That'd make it easy.

130
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:09,950
Master, you're right.

131
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,920
I was joking. You took that seriously?

132
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:18,150
No, there is a way to make him say it himself.

133
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:19,380
But I can't ask him.

134
00:11:19,380 --> 00:11:21,510
No matter how close we are,

135
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:25,570
if I bring it up, he'll get suspicious immediately.

136
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:31,050
So, I need someone else,

137
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:36,430
someone who can get information out of him for me and open up his mouth.

138
00:11:37,450 --> 00:11:40,700
Then it has to be the people closest to him.

139
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:45,410
His principal wife, Jiang Xiang, was born into nobility and regards herself highly.

140
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:49,290
Even if you are of value to her, she'll still order you around like a dog.

141
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:51,050
The same goes for Zhuang Zhifu.

142
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:53,340
Besides, I've drawn too much attention.

143
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:56,690
Both Yang Zhen and Qu Jiao died because of me.

144
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:59,630
They won't trust me easily.

145
00:12:04,170 --> 00:12:06,550
So, that leaves one person.

146
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:09,200
Too bad Zhuang Zhixing is too weak.

147
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:12,490
Otherwise, he'd really be a solid choice.

148
00:12:14,940 --> 00:12:18,590
No. He is the best choice.

149
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:22,600
But everyone in the capital knows the Marquis looks down on him.

150
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,070
Are you sure you want him?

151
00:12:24,070 --> 00:12:27,670
Yes. I'll help him earn the Marquis's favor and trust.

152
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:30,000
Then he can ask for me.

153
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,550
Why would he help you?

154
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:35,240
Because people move for one thing: Self-interest.

155
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:37,170
And what do you have to offer?

156
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:40,690
I'll help him become the Marquis residence's heir.

157
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,100
The heir?

158
00:12:46,290 --> 00:12:49,050
Zhuang Zhifu is the legitimate son of the residence.

159
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:51,340
Zhuang Zhixing is just a lost cause.

160
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:53,630
How could he possibly compete?

161
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:57,550
The difficulty is precisely why he'll be tempted.

162
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:59,050
I help him rise,

163
00:12:59,050 --> 00:13:01,170
and he helps me learn the Marquis's secret.

164
00:13:01,170 --> 00:13:02,720
It's very fair.

165
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,550
Besides, I heard his birth mother

166
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:07,200
was once deeply favored by the Marquis.

167
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:10,170
But both mother and son gradually got cast aside.

168
00:13:10,170 --> 00:13:13,600
That kind of fall from grace is hard to live with.

169
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:17,650
So, I believe he won't turn me down.

170
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:25,698
   

171
00:13:56,750 --> 00:14:02,550
   

172
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:10,160
   

173
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:15,850
All of you, leave.

